 UnfoldSim.closest_src  â€”  Method closest_src(coords_list::AbstractVector{<:AbstractVector}, pos) When applied to a vector of target coordinate vectors, return the index of the closest position in  pos  for each of the targets.  Returns Vector : Index of the closest position in  pos  for each vector in  coords_list . Examples julia> positions = [0 0 0; 2 2 2; 3 3 3; 4 4 4];
